= 2013.1.1 =
Deze versie lost het probleem op waarbij NVDA vastliep when started if configured to use de Irish language, as well as including updates to translaties en some other bug fixes.

== Opgeloste Problemen ==
- Correct karakters are produced when typing in NVDA's own user interface while using een Koreaanse of Japanse invoermethod while it is de default method. (#2909)
- In Internet Explorer en other MSHTML controls, velden marked as containing een invalid entry are nu handled correctly. (#3256)
- NVDA loopt niet langer vast when started if it is configured to use de Irish language.


= 2013.1 =
Hoogtepunten in deze versie include een more intuitive en consistent laptop toetsenbord layout; basic support voor Microsoft PowerPoint; support voor long descriptions in web browsers; en support voor input of computer braille voor brailleleesregels which have een braille toetsenbord.

== Important ==

=== Nieuw Laptop Keyboard Layout ===
The laptop toetsenbord layout has been completely redesigned in order to make it more intuitive en consistent.
The nieuw layout uses de arrow keys in combinatie with de NVDA key en other modifiers voor review commands.

Please note de following changes to commonly used commands:
|| Name | Key |
| Say all | NVDA+a |
| Read current line | NVDA+l |
| Read current text selection | NVDA+shift+s |
| Report status bar | NVDA+shift+end |
In addition, among other changes, all of de object navigatie, text review, mouse click en synth settings ring commands have changed.
Please see de [Commands Quick Reference keyCommands.html] document voor de nieuw keys.


== Nieuwe Functies ==
- Basic support voor editing en reading Microsoft PowerPoint presentaties. (#501)
- Basic support voor reading en writing berichten in Lotus Notes 8.5. (#543)
- Ondersteuning voor automatic language switching when reading documenten in Microsoft Word. (#2047) 
- In Browse mode voor MSHTML (e.g. Internet Explorer) en Gecko (e.g. Firefox), de existance of long descriptions are nu announced. It's also possible to open de long description in een nieuw window by pressing NVDA+d. (#809)
- Notificaties in Internet Explorer 9 en hoger are nu spoken (such as content blocking or file downloads). (#2343)
- Automatic reporting of tabel row en kolom headers is nu supported voor browse mode documenten in Internet Explorer en other MSHTML controls. (#778)
- Nieuw language: Aragonese, Irish
- Nieuw braille translatie tabels: Danish grade 2, Korean grade 1. (#2737)
- Ondersteuning voor brailleleesregels connected via bluetooth on een computer running de Bluetooth Stack voor Windows by Toshiba. (#2419)
- Ondersteuning voor port selection when using Freedom Scientific displays (Automatic, USB or Bluetooth).
- Ondersteuning voor de BrailleNote family of notetakers from HumanWare when acting as een braille terminal voor een scherm reader. (#2012)
- Ondersteuning voor older models of Papenmeier BRAILLEX brailleleesregels. (#2679)
- Ondersteuning voor input of computer braille voor brailleleesregels which have een braille toetsenbord. (#808)
- Nieuw toetsenbord settings that allow  de choice voor whether NVDA should interrupt speech voor typed karakters and/or de Enter key. (#698)
- Ondersteuning voor several browsers based on Google Chrome: Rockmelt, BlackHawk, Comodo Dragon en SRWare Iron. (#2236, #2813, #2814, #2815)


== Veranderingen ==
- Updated liblouis braille translator to 2.5.2. (#2737)
- De laptop toetsenbord layout has been completely redesigned in order to make it more intuitive en consistent. (#804)
- Updated eSpeak speech synthesizer to 1.47.11. (#2680, #3124, #3132, #3141, #3143, #3172)


== Opgeloste Problemen ==
- De quick navigatie keys voor jumping to de next or previous separator in Browse Mode nu work in Internet Explorer en other MSHTML controls. (#2781)
- If NVDA falls back to eSpeak or no speech due to de configured speech synthesizer failing when NVDA starts, de configured choice is niet langer automatisch set to de fallback synthesizer. This means that now, de original synthesizer will be tried again next time NVDA starts. (#2589)
- If NVDA falls back to no braille due to de configured brailleleesregel failing when NVDA starts, de configured display is niet langer automatisch set to no braille. This means that now, de original display will be tried again next time NVDA starts. (#2264)
- In browse mode in Mozilla applicaties, updates to tabels are nu rendered correctly. For example, in updated cellen, row en kolom coordinates are reported en tabel navigatie works as it should. (#2784)
- In browse mode in web browsers, certain clickable unlabelled graphics which weren't previously rendered are nu rendered correctly. (#2838)
- Earlier en newer versions of SecureCRT are nu supported. (#2800)
- For input  methods such as Easy Dots IME under XP, de reading string is nu correctly reported.
- De candidate list in de Chinese Simplified Microsoft Pinyin input method under Windows 7 is nu correctly read when changing pages with left en right arrow, en when first opening it with Home.
- When custom symbol pronunciatie informatie is saved, de advanced "preserve" veld is niet langer removed. (#2852)
- When disabling automatic checking voor updates, NVDA niet langer has to be restarted in order voor de change to fully take effect.
- NVDA niet langer fails to start if een add-on cannot be removed due to its directory currently being in use by another applicatie. (#2860)
- Tab labels in DropBox's preferences dialog can nu be seen with Flat Review.
- If de input language is changed to something other than de default, NVDA nu detects keys correctly voor commands en input help mode.
- For languages such as German where de + (plus) sign is een single key on de toetsenbord, it is nu possible to bind commands to it by using de word "plus". (#2898)
- In Internet Explorer en other MSHTML controls, block quotes are nu reported where appropriate. (#2888)
- De HumanWare Brailliant BI/B series brailleleesregel driver can nu be selected when de display is connected via Bluetooth but has never been connected via USB.
- Filtering elements in de Browse Mode Elements list with uppercase filter text nu returns case-insensitive results just like lowercase rather than nothing at all. (#2951)
- In Mozilla browsers, browse mode can again be used when Flash content is focused. (#2546)
- When using een contracted braille tabel en expand to computer braille voor de word at de cursor is ingeschakeld, de braille cursor is nu positioned correctly when located after een word wherein een karakter is represented by multiple braille cellen (e.g. capital sign, letter sign, number sign, etc.). (#2947)
- Text selection is nu correctly shown on een brailleleesregel in applicaties such as Microsoft word 2003 en Internet Explorer edit controls.
- It is again possible to select text in een backward direction in Microsoft Word while Braille is ingeschakeld.
- When reviewing,  backspacing or deleting karakters  In Scintilla edit controls, NVDA correctly announces multibyte karakters. (#2855)
- NVDA will niet langer fail to install when de user's profile path contains certain multibyte karakters. (#2729)
- Reporting of groups voor List View controls (SysListview32) in 64-bit applicaties niet langer causes een error.
- In browse mode in Mozilla applicaties, text content is niet langer incorrectly treated as editable in some rare cases. (#2959)
- In IBM Lotus Symphony en OpenOffice, moving de caret nu moves de review cursor if appropriate.
- Adobe Flash content is nu accessible in Internet Explorer in Windows 8. (#2454)
- Fixed Bluetooth support voor Papenmeier Braillex Trio. (#2995)
- Fixed inability to use certain Microsoft Speech API version 5 voices such as Koba Speech 2 voices. (#2629)
- In applicaties using de Java Access Bridge, brailleleesregels are nu updated correctly when de caret moves in editable text velden . (#3107)
- Support de formulier landmark in browse mode documenten that support landmarks. (#2997) 
- De eSpeak synthesizer driver nu handles reading by karakter more appropriately (e.g. announcing een foreign letter's name or value rather than just its sound or generic name). (#3106)
- NVDA niet langer fails to copy user settings voor use on logon en other secure schermen when de user's profile path contains non-ASCII karakters. (#3092)
- NVDA niet langer freezes when using Asian karakter input in some .NET applicaties. (#3005)
- it is nu possible to use browse mode voor pages in Internet Explorer 10 when in standards mode; e.g. www.gmail.com login page. (#3151)


