= 2012.3 =
Hoogtepunten in deze versie include support voor Asian karakter input; experimental support voor aanraakschermen on Windows 8; reporting of page numbers en improved support voor tabels in Adobe Reader; tabel navigatie commands in focused tabel rows en Windows list-view controls; support voor several more brailleleesregels; en reporting of row en kolom headers in Microsoft Excel.

== Nieuwe Functies ==
- NVDA can nu support Asian karakter input using IME en text service input methods in all applicaties, Including:
 - Reporting en navigatie of candidate lists;
 - Reporting en navigatie of composition strings; and
 - Reporting of reading strings.
- De presence of underline en strikethrough is nu reported in Adobe Reader documenten. (#2410)
- When de Windows Sticky Keys function is ingeschakeld, de NVDA modifier key will nu behave like other modifier keys. This allows you to use de NVDA modifier key without needing to hold it down while you press other keys. (#230)
- Automatic reporting of kolom en row headers is nu supported in Microsoft Excel. Press NVDA+shift+c to set de row containing kolom headers en NVDA+shift+r to set de kolom containing row headers. Press either command twice in quick succession to clear de setting. (#1519)
- Ondersteuning voor HIMS Braille Sense, Braille EDGE en SyncBraille brailleleesregels. (#1266, #1267)
- When Windows 8 Toast notificaties appear, NVDA will report them if reporting of help balloons is ingeschakeld. (#2143)
- Experimental support voor Touch schermen on Windows 8, including:
 - Reading text directly under your finger while moving it around
 - Many gestures voor performing object navigatie, text review, en other NVDA commands.
- Ondersteuning voor VIP Mud. (#1728)
- In Adobe Reader, if een tabel has een summary, it is nu presented. (#2465)
- In Adobe Reader, tabel row en kolom headers can nu be reported. (#2193, #2527, #2528)
- Nieuw languages: Amharic, Korean, Nepali, Slovenian.
- NVDA can nu read auto complete suggestions when entering email addresses in Microsoft Outlook 2007. (#689)
- Nieuw eSpeak voice variants: Gene, Gene2. (#2512)
- In Adobe Reader, page numbers can nu be reported. (#2534)
 - In Reader XI, page labels are reported where present, reflecting changes to page numbering in different sections, etc. In earlier versions, this is not possible en only sequential page numbers are reported.
- It is nu possible to reset NVDA's configuratie to factory defaults either by pressing NVDA+control+r three times quickly or by choosing Reset to Factory Defaults from de NVDA menu. (#2086)
- Ondersteuning voor de Seika Version 3, 4 en 5 en Seika80 brailleleesregels from Nippon Telesoft. (#2452)
- De first en last top routing knoppen on Freedom Scientific PAC Mate en Focus Brailleleesregels can nu be used to scroll  backward en forward. (#2556)
- Many more features are supported on Freedom Scientific Focus Brailleleesregels such as advance bars, rocker bars en certain dot combinaties voor common actions. (#2516)
- In applicaties using IAccessible2 such as Mozilla applicaties, tabel row en kolom headers can nu be reported outside of browse mode. (#926)
- Preliminary support voor de document control in Microsoft Word 2013. (#2543)
- Text alignment can nu be reported in applicaties using IAccessible2 such as Mozilla applicaties. (#2612)
- When een tabel row or standard Windows list-view control with multiple kolommen is focused, you can nu use de tabel navigatie commands to access individual cellen. (#828)
- Nieuw braille translatie tabels: Estonian grade 0, Portuguese 8 dot computer braille, Italian 6 dot computer braille. (#2319, #2662)
- If NVDA is installed on de system, directly opening een NVDA add-on package (e.g. from Windows Explorer or after downloading in een web browser) will install it into NVDA. (#2306)
- Ondersteuning voor newer models of Papenmeier BRAILLEX brailleleesregels. (#1265)
- Position informatie (e.g. 1 of 4) is nu reported voor Windows Explorer list items on Windows 7 en hoger. This also includes any UIAutomatie controls that support de itemIndex en itemCount custom properties. (#2643)


== Veranderingen ==
- In de NVDA Review Cursor preferences dialog, de Follow toetsenbord focus option has been renamed to Follow system focus voor consistency with terminology used elsewhere in NVDA.
- When braille is tethered to review en de cursor is on een object which is not een text object (e.g. een editable text veld), cursor routing keys will nu activate de object. (#2386)
- De Save Settings On Exit option is nu on by default voor nieuw configuraties.
- When updating een previously installed copy of NVDA, de desktop shortcut key is niet langer forced back to control+alt+n if it was manually changed to something different by de user. (#2572)
- De add-ons list in de Add-ons Manager nu shows de package name before its status. (#2548)
- If installing de same or another version of een currently installed add-on, NVDA will ask if you wish to update de add-on, rather than just showing een error en aborting installatie. (#2501)
- Object navigatie commands (except de report current object command) nu report with less verbosity. You can still obtain de extra informatie by using de report current object command. (#2560)
- Updated liblouis braille translator to 2.5.1. (#2319, #2480, #2662, #2672)
- De NVDA Key Commands Quick Reference document has been renamed to Commands Quick Reference, as it nu includes touch commands as well as toetsenbord commands.
- De Elements list in Browse mode will nu remember de last element type shown (e.g. links, headings or landmarks) each time de dialog is shown within de same session of NVDA. (#365)
- Most Metro apps in Windows 8 (e.g. Mail, Calendar) niet langer activate Browse Mode voor de entire app.
- Updated Handy Tech BrailleDriver COM-Server to 1.4.2.0.


