- UI Automatie text controls (e.g.  de search veld in de Windows 7 Start Menu) are nu  correctly announced when moving de mouse over them rather than staying silent.
- Keyboard layout changes are niet langer reported during say all, which was particularly problematic voor multilingual documenten including Arabic text. (#1676)
- De entire content of some UI Automatie editable text controls (e.g. de Search Box in de Windows 7/8 Start Menu) is niet langer announced every time it changes.
- When moving between groups on de Windows 8 start scherm, unlabeled groups niet langer announce their first tile as de name of de group. (#2658)
- When opening de Windows 8 start scherm, de focus is correctly placed on de first tile, rather than jumping to de root of de start scherm which can confuse navigatie. (#2720)
- NVDA will niet langer fail to start when de user's profile path contains certain multibyte karakters. (#2729)
- In browse mode in Google Chrome, de text of tabs is nu rendered correctly.
- In browse mode, menu knoppen are nu reported correctly.
- In OpenOffice.org/LibreOffice Calc, reading spreadsheet cellen nu works correctly. (#2765)
- NVDA can again function in de Yahoo! Mail bericht list when used from Internet Explorer. (#2780)


