= 2012.2.1 =
Deze versie addresses  several potential security issues (by upgrading Python to 2.7.3).


= 2012.2 =
Hoogtepunten in deze versie include een in-built installer en  portable  creatie feature, automatic updates, easy management of nieuw NVDA add-ons, announcement of graphics in Microsoft Word, support voor Windows 8 Metro style apps, en several important bug fixes. 

== Nieuwe Functies ==
- NVDA can nu automatisch check for, download en install updates. (#73)
- Extending NVDA's functionality  has been made easier with de addition of een Add-ons Manager (found under Tools in de NVDA menu) allowing you to install en uninstall nieuw NVDA add-on packages (.nvda-addon files) containing plugins en drivers. Note de Add-on manager does not show older custom plugins en drivers manually copied in to your configuratie directory. (#213)
- Many more common NVDA features nu work in Windows 8 Metro style apps when using een installed release  of NVDA, including speaking of typed karakters, en browse mode voor web documenten (includes support voor metro version of Internet Explorer 10). Portable copies of NVDA cannot access metro style apps. (#1801) 
- In browse mode documenten (Internet Explorer, Firefox, etc.), you can nu  jump to de start en past de end of certain containing elements (such as lists en tabels) with shift+, en , respectively. (#123)
- Nieuw language: Greek.
- Graphics en alt text are nu reported in Microsoft Word Documenten. (#2282, #1541)


== Veranderingen ==
- Announcement of cell coordinates in Microsoft Excel is nu after de content rather than before, en is nu only included   if de report tabels en report tabel cell coordinates settings are ingeschakeld in de Document formatting settings dialog. (#320)
- NVDA is nu distributed in one package. Rather than separate portable en installer versions, there is nu just one file that, when run, will start een temporary copy of NVDA en will allow you to install or generate een portable distribution. (#1715)
- NVDA is nu always installed in to Program Files on all systems. Updating een previous install will also automatisch move it if it was not previously installed there.


