= 2012.1 =
Hoogtepunten in deze versie include features voor more fluent reading of braille; indicatie of document formatting in braille; access to much more formatting informatie en improved performance in Microsoft Word; en support voor de iTunes Store.

== Nieuwe Functies ==
- NVDA can announce de number of leading tabs en spaces of de current line in de order that they are entered. This can be ingeschakeld by selecting report line indentatie in de document formatting dialogue. (#373)
- NVDA can nu detect key presses generated from alternative toetsenbord input emulatie such as on-scherm toetsenborden en speech recognition software.
- NVDA can nu detect colors in Windows command consoles.
