- In de Keyboard Settings dialog, de toetsenbord layout names are nu presented in de configured NVDA language instead of always in English. (#558)
- Fixed een issue where some items were rendered as empty in Adobe Reader documenten; e.g. de links in de tabel of contents of de Apple iPhone IOS 4.1 User Guide.
