- Veranderingen on dynamic pages in Gecko2 documenten (E.g. Firefox 4) while multiple tabs are open are nu properly reflected by NVDA. Previously only changes in de first tab were reflected. (Mozilla bug 610985)
- NVDA can nu properly announce de suggestions voor grammar en punctuatie errors in Microsoft Word spell check dialog. (#704)
- In Internet Explorer en other MSHTML controls, NVDA niet langer presents destinatie anchors as empty links in its virtual buffer. Instead, these anchors are hidden as they should be. (#1326)
