- On ALVA BC640/BC680 brailleleesregels, NVDA niet langer disregards display keys that are still held down after another key is released.
- Adobe Reader X niet langer crashes after leaving de untagged document options before de processing dialog appears. (#1218)
- NVDA nu switches to de appropriate brailleleesregel driver when you revert to saved configuratie. (#1346)
- De Visual Studio 2008 Project Wizard is read correctly again. (#974)
- NVDA niet langer completely fails to work in applicaties which contain non-ASCII karakters in their executable name. (#1352)
- When reading by line in AkelPad with word wrap ingeschakeld, NVDA niet langer reads de first karakter of de following line at de end of de current line.
