= 2010.2 =
Notable features of deze versie include greatly simplified object navigatie; virtual buffers voor Adobe Flash content; access to many previously inaccessible controls by retrieving text written naar het scherm; flat review of scherm text; support voor IBM Lotus Symphony documenten; reporting of tabel row en kolom headers in Mozilla Firefox; en significantly improved user documentatie.

== Nieuwe Functies ==
- Navigating through objects with de review cursor has been greatly simplified. De review cursor nu excludes objects which aren't useful to de user; i.e. objects only used voor layout purposes en unavailable objects.
- In applicaties using de Java Access Bridge (including OpenOffice.org), formatting can nu be reported in text controls. (#358, #463)
- When moving de mouse over cellen in Microsoft Excel, NVDA will appropriately announce them.
