- Help balloons are nu displayed in braille when they appear. (#652)
- Added een driver voor de MDV Lilli brailleleesregel. (#241)
- When selecting een entire row or kolom in Microsoft Excel with de shortcut keys shift+space en control+space, de nieuw selection is nu reported. (#759)
- Tabel row en kolom headers can nu be reported. This is configurable from de Document Formatting preferences dialog.
 - Currently, this is supported in documenten in Mozilla applicaties such as Firefox (version 3.6.11 en later) en Thunderbird (version 3.1.5 en later). (#361)
- Introduced commands voor flat review: (#58)
 - NVDA+numpad7  switches to flat review, placing de review cursor at de position of de current object, allowing you  to review het scherm (of een document als er een is geopend) with de text review commands.
 - NVDA+numpad1 moves de review cursor into de object represented by de text at  de position of de review cursor, allowing you to navigate by object from that point.
- Current NVDA user settings can be  copied to be used on secure Windows schermen such as de logon en UAC schermen by pressing een knop in de General Settings dialog. (#730)
- Ondersteuning voor Mozilla Firefox 4.
- Ondersteuning voor Microsoft Internet Explorer 9.


== Veranderingen ==
- De sayAll by Navigator object (NVDA+numpadAdd), navigator object next in flow (NVDA+shift+numpad6) en navigator object previous in flow (NVDA+shift+numpad4) commands have been removed voor de time being, due to bugginess en to free up de keys voor other possible features.
- In de NVDA Synthesizer dialog, only de display name of de synthesizer is nu listed. Previously, it was prefixed by de driver's name, which is only relevant internally.
- When in embedded applicaties or virtual buffers inside another virtualBuffer (e.g. Flash), you can nu  press nvda+control+space to move out of de embedded applicatie or virtual buffer to de containing document. Previously nvda+space  was used voor this. Nu nvda+space is specifically only voor toggling brows/focus modes on virtualBuffers.
- If de speech viewer (ingeschakeld under de tools menu) is given de focus (e.g. it was clicked in) nieuw text will not appear in de control until focus is moved away. This allows voor selecting de text with greater ease (e.g. voor copying).
- De Log Viewer en Python Console are maximised when activated.
- When focusing on een worksheet in Microsoft Excel en there is more than one cell selected, de selection range is announced, rather than just de active cell. (#763)
- Saving configuratie en changing of particular sensitive options is nu disabled when running on de logon, UAC en other secure Windows schermen.
- Updated eSpeak speech synthesiser to 1.44.03.
- If NVDA is already running, activating de NVDA shortcut on de desktop (which includes pressing control+alt+n) will restart NVDA.
- Removed de report text under de mouse checkbox from de Mouse settings dialog en replaced it with een Enable mouse tracking checkbox, which better matches de toggle mouse tracking script (NVDA+m). 
- Updates to de laptop toetsenbord layout so that it includes all commands available in de desktop layout en works correctly on non-English toetsenborden. (#798, #800)
- Significant verbeteringen en updates to de user documentatie, including documentatie of de laptop toetsenbord commands en synchronisatie of de Keyboard Commands Quick Reference with de User Guide. (#455)
- Updated liblouis braille translator to 2.1.1. Notably, this fixes some issues related to Chinese braille as well as karakters which are undefined in de translatie tabel. (#484, #499)


