- When de tabel navigatie commands are used outside of een tabel in Microsoft Word, "edge of tabel" is niet langer spoken after "not in tabel". (#921)
- When de tabel navigatie commands cannot move due to being at de edge of een tabel in Microsoft Word, "edge of tabel" is nu spoken in de configured NVDA language rather than always in English. (#921)
- In Outlook Express, Windows Mail en Windows Live Mail, de state of de checkboxes in bericht rules lists is nu reported. (#576)
- De description of bericht rules can nu be read in Windows Live Mail 2010.


= 2010.1 =
Deze versie focuses primarily on bug fixes en verbeteringen to de user experience, including some significant stability fixes.

== Nieuwe Functies ==
- NVDA niet langer fails to start on een system with no audio output devices. Obviously, een brailleleesregel or de Silence synthesiser in conjunction with de Speech Viewer will need to be used voor output in this case. (#425)
- Een report landmarks checkbox has been added to de Document Formatting settings dialog which allows you to configure whether NVDA should announce landmarks in web documenten. For compatibility with de previous release, de option is on by default.
- If speak command keys is ingeschakeld, NVDA will nu announce de names of multimedia keys (e.g. play, stop, home page, etc.) on many toetsenborden when they are pressed. (#472)
- NVDA nu announces de word being deleted when pressing control+backspace in controls that support it. (#491)
- Arrow keys can nu be used in de Web formator window to navigate en read de text. (#452)
- De entry list in de Microsoft Office Outlook address book is nu supported.
- NVDA better supports embedded editable (design mode) documenten in Internet Explorer. (#402)
- een nieuw script (nvda+shift+numpadMinus) allows you to move de system focus to de current navigator object.
- Nieuw scripts to lock en unlock de left en right mouse knoppen. Useful voor performing drag en drop operaties. shift+numpadDivide to lock/unlock de left, shift+numpadMultiply to lock/unlock de right.
- Nieuw braille translatie tabels: German 8 dot computer braille, German grade 2, Finnish 8 dot computer braille, Chinese (Hong Kong, Cantonese), Chinese (Taiwan, Manderin). (#344, #369, #415, #450)
- It is nu possible to disable de creatie of de desktop shortcut (and thus de shortcut key) when installing NVDA. (#518)
- NVDA can nu use IAccessible2 when present in 64 bit applicaties. (#479)
- Improved support voor live regions in Mozilla applicaties. (#246)
- De NVDA Controller Client API is nu provided to allow applicaties to control NVDA; e.g. to speak text, silence speech, display een bericht in Braille, etc.
- Informatie en error berichten are nu read in de logon scherm in Windows Vista en Windows 7. (#506)
- In Adobe Reader, PDF interactive formulieren developed with Adobe LiveCycle are nu supported. (#475)
- In Miranda IM, NVDA nu automatisch reads incoming berichten in chat windows if reporting of dynamic content changes is ingeschakeld. Also, commands have been added to report de three most recent berichten (NVDA+control+number). (#546)
- Input text velden are nu supported in Adobe Flash content. (#461)


== Veranderingen ==
- De extremely verbose toetsenbord help bericht in de Windows 7 Start menu is niet langer reported.
- De Display synth has nu been replaced with een nieuw Speech Viewer. To activate it, choose Speech Viewer from de Tools menu. De speech viewer can be used independently of what ever speech synthesizer you are using. (#44)
- Messages on de brailleleesregel will automatisch be dismissed if de user presses een key that results in een change such as de focus moving. Previously de bericht would always stay around voor its configured time.
- Setting whether braille should be tethered to de focus or de review cursor (NVDA+control+t) can nu be also set from de braille settings dialog, en is also nu saved in de user's configuratie.
- Updated eSpeak speech synthesiser to 1.43.
- Updated liblouis braille translator to 1.8.0.
- In virtual buffers, de reporting of elements when moving by karakter or word has been greatly improved. Previously, een lot of irrelevant informatie was reported en de reporting was very different to that when moving by line. (#490)
- De Control key nu simply stops speech like other keys, rather than pausing speech. To pause/resume speech, use de shift key.
- Tabel row en kolom counts are niet langer announced when reporting focus changes, as this announcement is rather verbose en usually not useful.


== Opgeloste Problemen ==
- NVDA niet langer fails to start if UI Automatie support appears to be available but fails to initialise voor some reason. (#483)
- De entire contents of een tabel row is niet langer sometimes reported when moving focus inside een cell  in Mozilla applicaties. (#482)
- NVDA niet langer lags voor een long time when expanding tree view items that contain een very large amount of sub-items.
- When listing SAPI 5 voices, NVDA nu tries to detect buggy voices en excludes them from de Voice Settings dialog en synthesiser settings ring. Previously, when there was just one problematic voice, NVDA's SAPI 5 driver would sometimes fail to start.
