- In virtual buffers, row/kolom coordinates are niet langer incorrectly read voor row en kolom headers when reporting of tabels is disabled.
- In virtual buffers, row/kolom coordinates are nu correctly read when you leave een tabel en then re-enter de same tabel cell without visiting another cell first; e.g. pressing upArrow then downArrow on de first cell of een tabel. (#378)
- Blank lines in Microsoft Word documenten en  Microsoft HTML edit controls are nu shown appropriately on brailleleesregels. Previously NVDA was displaying de current sentence on de display, not de current line voor these situaties. (#420)
- Multiple security fixes when running NVDA at Windows logon en on other secure desktops. (#515)
- De cursor position (caret) is nu correctly updated when performing een Say All that goes off de onderkant van het scherm, in standard Windows edit velden en Microsoft Word documenten. (#418)
