- Fixes to de laptop toetsenbord layout. (#517)
- When Braille is tethered to review when you focus on een Dos console window, de review cursor can nu properly navigate de text in de console.
- While working with TeamTalk3 or TeamTalk4 Classic, de VU meter progress bar in de main window is niet langer announced as it updates. Also, special karakters can be read properly in de incoming chat window.
- Items are niet langer spoken twice in de Windows 7 Start Menu. (#474)
- Activating same-page links in Firefox 3.6 appropriately moves de cursor in de virtualBuffer to de correct place on de page.
- Fixed de issue where some text was not rendered in Adobe Reader in certain PDF documenten.
- NVDA niet langer incorrectly speaks certain numbers separated by een dash; e.g. 500-1000. (#547)
- In Windows XP, NVDA niet langer causes Internet Explorer to freeze when toggling checkboxes in Windows Update. (#477)
